#. 4.0->settings-schema.json->hover-peek-thumbnail->description
#. 6.0->settings-schema.json->hover-peek-thumbnail->description
#. 5.4->settings-schema.json->hover-peek-thumbnail->description
msgid "Show a full size window preview when hovering over a Thumbnail"
msgstr ""
"Vis vinduesforhåndsvisning i fuld størrelse, når musen holdes over en "
"miniature"

#. 4.0->settings-schema.json->hover-peek-thumbnail->tooltip
#. 6.0->settings-schema.json->hover-peek-thumbnail->tooltip
#. 5.4->settings-schema.json->hover-peek-thumbnail->tooltip
msgid ""
"If enabled, a full size preview window will appear when the mouse pointer is "
"hovering over a Thumbnail menu item. The delay before the preview appears is "
"controlled by an option under the Advanced tab"
msgstr ""
"Hvis denne funktion er aktiveret, vises et forhåndsvisningsvindue i fuld "
"størrelse, når musemarkøren holdes over et miniaturemenuelement. Ventetiden, "
"før forhåndsvisningen vises, styres via en indstilling under fanebladet "
"“Avanceret”."

#. 4.0->settings-schema.json->no-click-activate-thumbnail->description
#. 6.0->settings-schema.json->no-click-activate-thumbnail->description
#. 5.4->settings-schema.json->no-click-activate-thumbnail->description
msgid "Automatic focus change when leaving the Thumbnail menu"
msgstr "Automatisk fokusskifte når miniaturemenuen forlades"

#. 4.0->settings-schema.json->no-click-activate-thumbnail->tooltip
#. 6.0->settings-schema.json->no-click-activate-thumbnail->tooltip
#. 5.4->settings-schema.json->no-click-activate-thumbnail->tooltip
msgid ""
"If enabled, the window associated with the Thumbnail menu item will get the "
"focus when the mouse pointer leaves the menu. Leaving the menu with Ctrl or "
"Shift held or leaving from either end of the menu will leave the focus "
"unchanged. This option is typically used in conjunction with the preview "
"hovering option above."
msgstr ""
"Hvis denne indstilling er aktiveret, får vinduet associeret med "
"miniaturemenuelementet fokus, når musemarkøren forlader panelet. Hvis du "
"forlader vindueslisten med Ctrl- eller Skift-tasten nede, eller fra den "
"eller anden side af menuen, forbliver fokus uændret. Denne indstilling "
"bruges typisk sammen med indstillingen for forhåndsvisning ved musemarkørens "
"placering ovenfor."

